.TH IIPFLE 6 "2023-04-20" "ENSIIE "IPFL12 22/23"
.SH NAME
main.bin \- utility tools for 2A & 3A programs
.SH SYNOPSIS
main.bin [1/2] [input.prog]
.br
main.bin 3 [message]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Modes 1 & 2 : this mode converts a 2A (mode 1) or 3A (mode 2) program into clear text.
.br
Mode 3 : this mode converts clear text into a 2A program.
.br
The result is output to the standard output.
.SH EXAMPLES
Example files are provided in the ./tests directory :
.br
	invert.prog        ) for testing the invert function
.br
	rep.prog           ) for testing the repeat function
.br
	delete.prog        ) for testing the delete & repeat functions
.br
	message_3aien.prog ) 2nd part introductive message
.br
	lorem, lorem.prog  ) conversion of plain text into 2A
.SH BUGS
none?
